Indroduction:

This lora is supposed to represent zheng's artstyle and... Khem. Features.

Model used for previews: DivineEleganceMix V4

Embeddings used for preview: EasyNegative and Bad-Hands-3

Artist's main features:

  • Thick bodies

  • Large/huge breasts

  • Large/huge penises

Recommendations:

  • 1.0 - 0.8 weight for most models

  • See relevant tag tips

  • (Anime / Tone Mapped / Flat Color:1.2) is also a good idea

    • You can use it separately or at the same time

Relevant genital tag tips:

You can adjust tag weights by placing it in brackets and specify value, like (Bulge:1.4), where 1.4 is modifier. Base tag weight is 1.0 when you're putting it in your prompt box.

Tags with brackets below are optional but may change result a lot.

  • (Full-package) Futanari + Pussy for penis and pussy

    • Might be uselful for From Behind view

  • Backsack for testicles from behind

    • Flaccid are not so good (bad, acually, will be improved later)

  • Large | Huge | Gigantic Testicles for testicles size

  • Sagging | Hanging | Resting Testicles for testicles state

    • Sagging for regular Zheng-style saggy testicles

    • Hanging for more saggy and low-positioned testicles

    • Resting for on-surface state while sitting (like breast rest)

  • Bulge + Futanari for bulges (nothing more needed)

  • Female Pubic Hair | Excessive Pubic Hair | Stray Pubic Hair for pubes

Why it's so hard?

  • Some ot these tags are not present on booru tags

  • It's better to have knowledge and control over LoRA you use

Can't get gigantic penis!

LoRA won't produce futas all the time (just don't prompt futa/penis), so you could generate regular cute funny-faced girls.

Credits:

Trained on NAI Anime Full. Dataset of 280 pictures. 8 Epochs. Clip Skip - 2.

Really BIG | LARGE | HUGE | GIGANTIC thanks to:

  • Zheng for beautiful artwork

  • Some good folks from Discord server

  • You, for reading, downloading and reviewing this LoRA

• Removed watermarks on whole dataset

A quick explanation why there is no generation data:
- After the last update on CivitAI any generation data can't be loaded from png meta, and when you're editint post for new version, you can't change it. If it would work after releasing, i would manually add it as soon as possible.

- Also, would upload more images soon, as always. So, just added some quick gens.
